{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"df10c25f88","title":"和刘晓、何长工的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d20f2afc53","index":0,"year":1934,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"df10c25f88"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8e331f2711","type":"paragraph","text":"和刘晓、何长工的谈话！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"df10c25f88"},{"id":"3fd626dd8a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1934年6月）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"df10c25f88"},{"id":"09a4270c58","type":"paragraph","text":"这一有利时机，利用敌人内部的争斗，发展壮大自己的力量。不能只知道“御敌人于国门之外”的死打硬拼，也要利用反动派之间的矛盾，加强统一战线工作。一面要依靠群众，发动群众，组织游击队，开展游击战争；一面可加派化装小分队，潜入陈济棠管区，宣传抗日救国、枪口一致对外的道理，促使陈军反蒋抗日。根据前线情况，可以把钩门岭一带部队抽下来进行整训，缓和前线的局势，并可积蓄我军力量，以备不膜。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"df10c25f88"},{"id":"ecc56ff9c9","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东在站塘等地调查后回到文武坝，和粤赣省委书记刘晓及","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"df10c25f88"}],"page":{"id":"57b58a5459","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"df10c25f88","start":37,"end":37}}}},"__N_SSG":true}